      "side": 1,
      "message": "I don\u0027t think so; the heap is sorted by (nextSend, id); we need to drop the oldest batch by id, not by nextSend. We\u0027re using `id` as a reference for \"old\".\n\nI think the name of this method just sucks a bit.\n\nThe goal is:\n  * Given a potential id to be inserted\n  * Find the oldest-by-id batch in the heap\n  * Drop it, if it\u0027s older than the potential id to be inserted",
